'''热带风暴克里斯托瓦尔'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Cristobal}}）是[[2008年大西洋飓风季|2008年大西洋飓风季]]第3场获得命名的风暴，源于7月19日[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]近海的[[低压槽|低压槽]]。由于外界环境倾向有利，系统于当天下午达到热带风暴的最低标准。气旋始终位于海上，于7月21日从[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]以东经过时达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]100公里的最高强度。克里斯托瓦尔加速向东北方向沿[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]平行移动，于7月23日在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]附近转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。

由于强度较小，并且没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，风暴产生的影响仅限于部分地区的中等程度降水。北卡罗莱纳州[[威尔明顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔明顿]]降下87毫米雨量，引发轻度洪灾。此外，克里斯托瓦尔的温带残留还在新斯科舍产生降雨，导致部分街道和地下室被淹。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Cristobal 2008 track.png}}
2008年7月14日，一条延伸到[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]北部上空并逐渐减弱的地表[[低压槽|低压槽]]在该州各地上空产生[[雷暴|雷暴]]<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Walton | author2 = Cangialosi | date = 2008-07-14 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]]}}</ref>。7月15日，[[塔拉赫西|塔拉赫西]]附近有弱[[低气压|低气压区]]形成<ref>{{cite report | author = Huffman | date = 2008-07-15 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，这片低气压区还向东南移动进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Wallace | date = 2008-07-15 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。7月16日晚，系统从[[坦帕_(佛罗里达州)|坦帕]]附近的陆地上空穿过<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Walton | author2 = Tichacek | date = 2008-07-16 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，气象机构预计系统会因与陆地相互作用而无法得到发展<ref>{{cite report | author = Franklin | date = 2008-07-16 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，但到了7月17日晚，低气压区关联的[[对流|对流]]已有增长<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Blake | author2 = Knabb | date = 2008-07-17 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，系统组织结构迅速改善。7月18日晚，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]宣布有热带低气压正在形成<ref>{{cite report | author = Franklin | date = 2008-07-18 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，其对流逐渐围绕环流集中，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月19日凌晨3点在[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]][[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]东南方向约105公里海域归类为[[2008年大西洋飓风季|2008年大西洋飓风季]]的第三号热带低气压<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125406/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.001.shtml? | author = Franklin | date = 2008-07-19 | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Depression Three Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-19 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。

受东南和西北方向的[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，低气压缓慢朝东北方向移动，并因上层大气环境略趋有利而在7月19日下午达到热带风暴强度的最低标准<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Blake | author2 = Knabb | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal Discussion Number 4 | year = 2008 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125445/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。气旋起初组织结构较为混乱，深层对流也很少<ref>{{cite report | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal Discussion Number 5 | year = 2008 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125446/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.005.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>，中到上层大气中干燥的空气也令系统无法立即强化<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Knabb | author2 = Blake | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal Discussion Number 7 | year = 2008 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.007.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125510/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.007.shtml | date =  }}</ref>。但到了7月20日晚，[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动已有增长<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Blake | author2 = Knabb | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal Discussion Number 8 | year = 2008 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125510/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.008.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.008.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。克里斯托瓦尔从南、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]近海掠过，在此期间强度一直偏弱，也始终没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。7月21日，风暴在从[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）以东洋面经过时达到最高强度，成为强烈热带风暴，并因[[墨西哥湾暖流|墨西哥湾暖流]]的[[海面温度|温暖水温]]而得以保持强度，环流南部上空的对流有所增强<ref>{{cite report | author = Blake | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal Discussion Number 11 | year = 2008 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125524/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.011.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2008-07-23 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.011.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。7月21至22日，气旋行经海域水温逐渐降低，在此期间也开始加速向[[罗盘方位|东北偏东]]方向前进<ref>{{cite report | author = Rhome | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal Discussion Number 12 | year = 2008 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.013.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125526/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.013.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。7月22日下午，克里斯托瓦尔开始在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]以南洋面减弱，当晚的卫星图像显示中层中心已经同下层中心分离<ref>{{cite report | author = Blake | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal Discussion Number 16 | year = 2008 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125550/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.016.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.016.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。气旋的云层格局变得杂乱无章，风暴于7月23日完全转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。美国国家飓风中心于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}7月23日上午9点发布针对系统的最后一份公告。<ref>{{cite report | author = Rhome | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal Discussion Number 18 | year = 2008 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125600/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.018.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al03/al032008.discus.018.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:TD_Three_2008_July_19_1415Z.jpg|thumb]]
面对风暴的威胁，南卡罗莱纳州[[桑蒂河|南桑蒂河]]（{{lang|en|South Santee River}}）到北卡罗莱纳州和弗吉尼亚州边界之间的沿海地区接获[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]。7月20日，气旋远离陆地，警告相应中止。<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Tropical Storm Cristobal | date = 2008-12-15 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002011247/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL032008_Cristobal.pdf | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL032008_Cristobal.pdf | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | format = [[PDF|PDF]] }}</ref>北卡罗莱纳州部分地区收到洪水警报<ref>{{cite news | author = Bruce Smith | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal rumbles off the Carolinas | date = 2008-07-19 | publisher = USA Today | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024105335/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/topstories/2008-07-19-384465296_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/topstories/2008-07-19-384465296_x.htm | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]预计克里斯托瓦尔可能会产生大浪和[[离岸流|离岸流]]，建议人们不要下水游泳<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal Forms Off Coast | date = 2008-07-19 | publisher = CBS News | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103110555/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tropical-storm-cristobal-forms-off-coast/ | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tropical-storm-cristobal-forms-off-coast/ | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，[[加拿大环境部|加拿大环境部]]还向[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]多地发布降雨警报<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |title=Parts of Nova Scotia prepare for a downpour from tropical storm Cristobal |date=2008-07-22 |publisher=The Canadian Press |accessdate=2016-01-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160112115537/http://www.ngnews.ca/Arts-%26amp;-Life/2008-07-22/article-315747/Parts-of-Nova-Scotia-prepare-for-a-downpour-from-tropical-storm-Cristobal/1 |archivedate=2016-01-12 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.ngnews.ca/Arts-%26amp;-Life/2008-07-22/article-315747/Parts-of-Nova-Scotia-prepare-for-a-downpour-from-tropical-storm-Cristobal/1 }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
克里斯托瓦尔的前身令[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]普降小到中雨。[[威尔士湖_(佛罗里达州)|威尔士湖]]测得150毫米雨量，其中大部分都是在两小时内降下。突如其来的暴雨令排水渠阻塞，部分街道洪水泛滥。<ref>{{cite news |first=Bill |last=Bair |date=2008-07-18 |title=System Likely to Deliver More Rain to Polk |work=The Ledger |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212235927/http://www.theledger.com/article/20080718/NEWS/807180436/1374%26title%3DSystem_Likely_to_Deliver_More_Rain_to_Polk%23 |archivedate=2012-02-12 |accessdate=2016-01-12 |url=http://www.theledger.com/article/20080718/NEWS/807180436/1374&title=System_Likely_to_Deliver_More_Rain_to_Polk# }}</ref>淹没的街道上有40辆车进水，有些还被0.6米深的水淹没。洪灾对佛罗里达州造成的损失数额估计为1万美元。<ref name="FLNCDC">{{cite report | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2008 | title = Event Report for Florida Flash Flood}}此来源可以通过订阅美国国家气象数据中心的历史文献出版物获得，注意选择2008年7月的数据。</ref>气旋在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]产生88毫米雨量，南卡罗莱纳州也有66毫米<ref name="WPCSE">{{cite book | last = Roth | first = David M | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall in the Southeastern United States | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150723225359/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcsoutheast.html | deadurl = no | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcsoutheast.html | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | archivedate = 2015-07-23 }}</ref>。

7月20日，克里斯托瓦尔从北卡罗莱纳州以东掠过，引起轻度破坏。海岸沿线水位比正常水平要高0.3米<ref name="NCDC NC">{{cite report | title = Event Report for Storm Surge/Tide | year = 2008 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center}}此来源可以通过订阅美国国家气象数据中心的历史文献出版物获得，注意选择2008年7月的数据。</ref>，还出现强烈的潮汐<ref name="CBS News">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = As Cristobal Soaks N.C., Dolly Forms | date = 2008-07-20 | publisher = CBS News | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103110558/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/as-cristobal-soaks-nc-dolly-forms/ | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/as-cristobal-soaks-nc-dolly-forms/ }}</ref>。当地平均降雨量在13到38毫米之间，但经{{lang|en|[[NEXRAD|NEXRAD]]}}[[气象雷达|气象雷达]]数据估算，也有局部地区降雨量超过100毫米<ref name="NCDC NC" />。[[威尔明顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔明顿]]降下87毫米雨量，引发轻度洪灾。风暴大部分覆盖范围仍在开放海域，所以沿海地区风速约为每小时40公里。<ref>{{cite web | first = Estes | last = Thompson | title = Tropical Storm Cristobal brushes NC coast | year = 2008 | publisher = Associated Press | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160112150649/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/2008-07-19-cristobal_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/2008-07-19-cristobal_N.htm }}</ref>

克里斯托瓦尔的中心距[[加拿大海洋省份|加拿大海洋省份]]还有超过1天路程时，气旋前方的湿气经一片几乎保持静止的[[锋_(气象)|锋面天气系统]]加强，在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]产生暴雨<ref name="TCR" />。巴卡罗角（{{lang|en|Baccaro Point}}）测得多达224毫米雨量，[[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]]附近的[[桑布罗_(新斯科舍)|桑布罗]]（{{lang|en|Sambro}}）也有145毫米。降雨致使[[沙布尔角岛|沙布尔角]]地区部分地下室和街道被淹。<ref>{{cite report |author1=Fogarty |author2=Bowyer |title=Tropical Storm Cristobal Information Statement |date=2008-07-22 |publisher=Canadian Hurricane Centre |accessdate=2011-06-11 |url=http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20080722180403.Cristobal.txt.en |archivedate=2011-06-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611123520/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20080722180403.Cristobal.txt.en }}</ref>[[康涅狄克州|康涅狄克州]]一名水手的船在波涛汹涌的海上失事，他最终在哈利法克斯东南方向约250公里海域获救<ref>{{cite web |author=CBC News |title=Sailor rescued from Cristobal's stormy wrath |date=2008-07-23 |accessdate=2012-08-01 |url=http://www.cbc.ca/canada/story/2008/07/23/cristobal-sailor.html |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120801192723/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/story/2008/07/23/cristobal-sailor.html |archivedate=2012-08-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。风暴产生的最强风力一直位于海上，有浮标测得时速达93公里的阵风<ref name="TCR" />。

